<p id="_881e4f22-0471-f54b-a589-d59f10d740cd">Using the recommended value of the absorbing molecule <sup>127</sup>I<sub>2</sub>, <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
