  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>ii(lambda) ~~ 633 "unitsml(nm)"</asciimath></stem> and frequency differences listed in corresponding Table 1) one obtains</p>

<p id="_27c4a4f5-0a04-9f6e-5b39-2a238fa9218e" align="left"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
